1
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:39,920
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:42,840
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:43,470 --> 00:01:44,400
Tell me quickly,

4
00:01:44,539 --> 00:01:46,440
am I about to have a senior sister-in-law?

5
00:01:46,440 --> 00:01:48,330
Alright, let's not talk about this now.

6
00:01:48,330 --> 00:01:50,990
I heard you've been
frequently leaving the palace lately.

7
00:01:50,990 --> 00:01:53,050
Has Marquis Wu'an made any new moves?

8
00:01:53,270 --> 00:01:54,600
No.

9
00:01:59,350 --> 00:02:01,190
I met an interesting person.

10
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:05,200
It must be a young lady.

11
00:02:05,410 --> 00:02:06,400
Chi.

12
00:02:07,330 --> 00:02:08,039
It seems

13
00:02:08,509 --> 00:02:11,530
we don't know
whose wedding we'll be celebrating first.

14
00:02:11,530 --> 00:02:12,620
That's not right.

15
00:02:12,990 --> 00:02:14,660
Things aren't moving
that quickly between us.

16
00:02:14,660 --> 00:02:15,720
-Come on.
-Come on.

17
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:29,350
Today is the last day
of the art exhibition.

18
00:02:30,430 --> 00:02:31,510
After today,

19
00:02:32,070 --> 00:02:34,200
where else can I find Mr. Lin Yuan?

20
00:02:38,810 --> 00:02:39,660
Pack up the paintings

21
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,350
and return them
to Mr. Lin Yuan's residence.

22
00:02:41,350 --> 00:02:42,100
Move quickly,

23
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:42,360
Yes!

24
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:44,040
Don't leave anything behind.

25
00:02:47,290 --> 00:02:47,970
Hello.

26
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:49,970
Are you the person in charge?

27
00:02:50,100 --> 00:02:52,700
Would it be possible
for me to meet Mr. Lin Yuan?

28
00:02:54,110 --> 00:02:55,760
My master keeps a low profile

29
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:56,980
and doesn't like meeting strangers.

30
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:58,380
Miss, please go back home.

31
00:02:58,380 --> 00:02:59,400
Please, I beg you.

32
00:02:59,420 --> 00:03:00,440
I come here every day,

33
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,630
waiting here daily,

34
00:03:01,660 --> 00:03:03,230
just to see him once.

35
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:05,790
If I can't see him today,

36
00:03:07,290 --> 00:03:08,270
I won't leave.

37
00:03:10,980 --> 00:03:12,430
Sir, I can testify

38
00:03:12,690 --> 00:03:15,020
that this Miss truly comes here every day.

39
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:19,690
It seems you genuinely likes our master.

40
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:23,170
I'll make an exception this time.

41
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:24,180
Please follow me.

42
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:25,440
Thank you.

43
00:03:31,940 --> 00:03:32,720
Master.

44
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:35,020
There's a Miss who insists on seeing you.

45
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:43,840
How could you bring
someone here without permission?

46
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,770
You know I never receive visitors.

47
00:03:45,790 --> 00:03:47,450
Please don't blame your steward, Sir.

48
00:03:47,450 --> 00:03:49,810
I insisted that he bring me to see you.

49
00:03:51,270 --> 00:03:53,329
I've admired
your paintings for a long time.

50
00:03:53,329 --> 00:03:54,790
Meeting you today

51
00:03:54,810 --> 00:03:56,260
is truly a wish come true.

52
00:03:57,510 --> 00:03:58,360
You may go.

53
00:04:00,330 --> 00:04:01,010
Come.

54
00:04:01,670 --> 00:04:03,070
Please have a seat, Miss.

55
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,280
I've seen you before.

56
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,470
You've seen me?

57
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:13,080
Where? When?

58
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:15,940
How is it that I've never seen you?

59
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,890
Since the art exhibition opened,

60
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,740
you've come every day.

61
00:04:21,140 --> 00:04:22,650
When you gazed at my paintings.

62
00:04:22,650 --> 00:04:24,940
sometimes you were
with joy and excitement,

63
00:04:24,940 --> 00:04:26,710
sometimes with melancholy.

64
00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:30,750
You must be someone
who truly understands me,

65
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:32,840
and genuinely appreciates my work.

66
00:04:35,050 --> 00:04:37,120
I express my feelings through painting,

67
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:38,650
while you are able to

68
00:04:38,860 --> 00:04:41,850
feel what I feel, think what I think.

69
00:04:42,270 --> 00:04:44,020
To find someone so sincere,

70
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:45,430
I am deeply moved.

71
00:04:47,310 --> 00:04:48,960
So you really did notice me.

72
00:04:49,770 --> 00:04:50,980
To be honest with you,

73
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:53,210
I have admired you for a long time,

74
00:04:53,780 --> 00:04:55,440
traveling far to the capital,

75
00:04:55,650 --> 00:04:56,740
just to find you.

76
00:04:59,050 --> 00:05:02,570
Thank you for your
profound affection and friendship.

77
00:05:02,810 --> 00:05:05,290
I am deeply grateful.

78
00:05:05,310 --> 00:05:06,910
Being able to meet you today,

79
00:05:06,970 --> 00:05:08,700
makes everything worthwhile.

80
00:05:16,630 --> 00:05:16,770
[Liuhe Pavilion]

81
00:05:16,770 --> 00:05:17,780
Ke.

82
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:18,980
I found Mr. Lin Yuan,

83
00:05:18,980 --> 00:05:19,920
I met him.

84
00:05:20,800 --> 00:05:21,890
When?

85
00:05:22,930 --> 00:05:24,520
Where did you meet him?

86
00:05:27,150 --> 00:05:28,640
Tell me what happened.

87
00:05:28,660 --> 00:05:30,520
How did you suddenly run into him?

88
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:32,950
Ke.

89
00:05:33,550 --> 00:05:35,820
Mr. Lin Yuan is definitely not Mr. Lu.

90
00:05:36,230 --> 00:05:37,540
The real Mr. Lin Yuan

91
00:05:37,570 --> 00:05:39,870
is in his prime,
with an impressive presence,

92
00:05:39,870 --> 00:05:41,050
and he's not married.

93
00:05:41,050 --> 00:05:44,040
See? It's completely different
from what you were worried about.

94
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,370
Mr. Lin Yuan and I
truly have a connection.

95
00:05:49,170 --> 00:05:51,659
I'm just glad you figured out he's not Lu.

96
00:05:52,130 --> 00:05:54,030
Qiyue.

97
00:05:54,180 --> 00:05:55,570
You must get to know him properly

98
00:05:55,570 --> 00:05:57,230
before discussing marriage.

99
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,570
What are you talking about?

100
00:05:58,570 --> 00:05:59,510
I'm not stupid.

101
00:05:59,700 --> 00:06:02,100
I only said I admire him.

102
00:06:02,450 --> 00:06:04,050
I never mentioned marriage.

103
00:06:04,410 --> 00:06:06,990
And he asked to see me again.

104
00:06:07,230 --> 00:06:09,270
I'll listen to you and meet with him more,

105
00:06:09,270 --> 00:06:12,130
get to know him
better before making any decisions.

106
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:14,210
I need to think about

107
00:06:14,330 --> 00:06:15,790
what to talk about with him

108
00:06:16,540 --> 00:06:18,190
and what questions to ask.

109
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:21,820
What a coincidence.

110
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:24,750
Something feels off.

111
00:06:31,970 --> 00:06:33,250
[Shi Fa'ke]

112
00:06:42,830 --> 00:06:43,800
Lu,

113
00:06:43,820 --> 00:06:45,550
Qiyue said she met Mr. Lin Yuan.

114
00:06:45,790 --> 00:06:46,760
When

115
00:06:47,030 --> 00:06:48,090
and where did she meet him?

116
00:06:48,090 --> 00:06:50,130
You asked
the exact same questions as I did.

117
00:06:50,130 --> 00:06:52,750
She said Mr. Lin Yuan is in his prime,

118
00:06:52,770 --> 00:06:53,870
handsome and talented,

119
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:55,310
and even asked to see her again.

120
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:57,440
I think something's fishy about this.

121
00:06:58,230 --> 00:06:59,480
In his prime?

122
00:07:01,860 --> 00:07:03,990
Who's impersonating Mr. Lin Yuan?

123
00:07:04,850 --> 00:07:07,180
And why would he
pretend to be Mr. Lin Yuan?

124
00:07:13,060 --> 00:07:14,360
What are you thinking?

125
00:07:17,900 --> 00:07:19,700
This Mr. Lin Yuan is an impostor.

126
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,170
Why are you so certain he's fake?

127
00:07:23,190 --> 00:07:24,740
Ke, trust me,

128
00:07:25,210 --> 00:07:26,820
Miss Yan has definitely been deceived.

129
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:28,330
You must stop her
from rushing into marriage,

130
00:07:28,330 --> 00:07:29,180
or else

131
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:32,200
the consequences would be unimaginable.

132
00:07:34,230 --> 00:07:36,230
Lu, I believe you.

133
00:07:36,840 --> 00:07:38,370
I'll go find her right away.

134
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,590
Qiyue.

135
00:07:48,020 --> 00:07:50,030
I have something to discuss with you.

136
00:07:50,030 --> 00:07:52,200
Mr. Lin Yuan keeps a very low profile,

137
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:54,940
and Xibao Pavilion
has been selling his paintings for years.

138
00:07:54,940 --> 00:07:57,260
All these years, no one has ever seen him,

139
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:59,380
nor has he ever held an art exhibition.

140
00:07:59,380 --> 00:08:01,810
Now he suddenly
wants to hold an exhibition

141
00:08:01,890 --> 00:08:03,350
and is willing to meet you.

142
00:08:03,570 --> 00:08:05,700
There are too many coincidences here.

143
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:07,320
Something's not right about this,

144
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,650
you have to reconsider.

145
00:08:08,690 --> 00:08:10,800
Ke, you're overthinking this.

146
00:08:11,290 --> 00:08:13,850
Isn't this exactly what you call fate?

147
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:15,830
I'm a matchmaker,

148
00:08:15,980 --> 00:08:17,640
so of course I believe in fate.

149
00:08:18,230 --> 00:08:19,490
But Lu is convinced

150
00:08:19,510 --> 00:08:21,200
that he's a fake Mr. Lin Yuan.

151
00:08:21,220 --> 00:08:23,650
Ke, say no more.

152
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:27,560
Qiyue, you shouldn't dismiss what Lu says.

153
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,390
Ke,

154
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,140
he's the one you care about,

155
00:08:30,140 --> 00:08:31,910
so it's understandable that you trust him.

156
00:08:31,910 --> 00:08:33,360
But I have my own feelings,

157
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,820
and I have someone I care about too.

158
00:08:34,820 --> 00:08:36,470
Mr. Lin Yuan and I
are already connected by fate.

159
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:37,270
That's a fact.

160
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,409
Do you know his real name?

161
00:08:40,429 --> 00:08:41,360
Where is he from?

162
00:08:41,390 --> 00:08:42,230
What family members...

163
00:08:42,230 --> 00:08:42,919
Ke.

164
00:08:44,010 --> 00:08:46,110
Before, I thought Mr. Lin Yuan was Lu Chi,

165
00:08:46,110 --> 00:08:47,920
and I could understand when you said no.

166
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,860
But now I've found the real Mr. Lin Yuan,

167
00:08:49,860 --> 00:08:50,840
and you're still saying no.

168
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:51,820
What exactly do you want from me?

169
00:08:51,820 --> 00:08:53,300
Of course I want what's best for you.

170
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:53,730
No.

171
00:08:54,940 --> 00:08:55,790
You clearly never wanted

172
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:58,250
me to be with Mr. Lin Yuan
from the beginning.

173
00:09:01,230 --> 00:09:01,830
Qiyue.

174
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,250
Qiyue.

175
00:09:05,110 --> 00:09:09,750
[Zuixuan Restaurant]

176
00:09:09,860 --> 00:09:10,670
Here, drink up.

177
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:11,180
Not bad.

178
00:09:11,610 --> 00:09:12,870
Just a bit short on ingredients.

179
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:13,550
Yeah,

180
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:15,230
but the taste is really good.

181
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,540
It's quite peaceful here.

182
00:09:20,270 --> 00:09:21,590
Your recommendation is good.

183
00:09:21,590 --> 00:09:22,450
Here, try this.

184
00:09:27,130 --> 00:09:29,390
Sorry to keep you waiting, Sir. I'm late.

185
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:30,510
Not at all,

186
00:09:31,330 --> 00:09:33,990
waiting for a kindred spirit
is always worth it.

187
00:09:38,310 --> 00:09:38,690
Come.

188
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:41,380
Qiyue, please have a seat.

189
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:52,070
Qiyue, do you know who he is?

190
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,270
Ke.

191
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:54,620
Why are you here?

192
00:09:54,940 --> 00:09:56,920
This is Mr. Lin Yuan I told you about.

193
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:58,380
He is not Mr. Lin Yuan.

194
00:09:58,400 --> 00:09:59,580
He is Marquis Wu'an.

195
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:02,160
Ke, what are you talking about?

196
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:03,850
Miss,

197
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,230
what evidence do you have

198
00:10:05,230 --> 00:10:06,960
that I'm not Mr. Lin Yuan?

199
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:10,440
Stop pretending.

200
00:10:10,470 --> 00:10:11,140
You...

201
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:11,850
Ke.

202
00:10:12,410 --> 00:10:13,500
Please leave now.

203
00:10:13,610 --> 00:10:14,600
Qiyue.

204
00:10:19,780 --> 00:10:20,610
Please.

205
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:33,060
Actually, your friend was right.

206
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,060
I am indeed the Marquis Wu'an.

207
00:10:35,650 --> 00:10:37,380
And precisely because of this,

208
00:10:38,020 --> 00:10:39,210
I don't want to

209
00:10:39,230 --> 00:10:41,290
reveal my true identity to the world.

210
00:10:41,860 --> 00:10:43,920
If they all knew who I really am,

211
00:10:44,750 --> 00:10:46,400
they would surely assume

212
00:10:46,690 --> 00:10:48,420
that I'm using my power

213
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:50,650
to gain false fame.

214
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:52,140
How would anyone

215
00:10:52,160 --> 00:10:54,220
truly appreciate my paintings then?

216
00:10:57,900 --> 00:10:58,740
No wonder

217
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:02,250
there's such a sense
of solitude in your paintings.

218
00:11:03,350 --> 00:11:04,950
It truly is lonely at the top.

219
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:09,040
You understand me best.

220
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,370
Please, have a seat.

221
00:11:13,490 --> 00:11:14,620
Here, have some tea.

222
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:19,720
Qiyue,

223
00:11:20,250 --> 00:11:24,830
if that Miss still has doubts about me,

224
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:27,470
I hope you won't argue with her.

225
00:11:27,970 --> 00:11:29,500
I don't want to be the reason

226
00:11:30,090 --> 00:11:32,250
that affects your sisterhood.

227
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:34,800
It doesn't matter if I'm misunderstood,

228
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:37,530
but I don't want you
to suffer any grievance.

229
00:11:45,810 --> 00:11:47,310
Sir, please don't worry.

230
00:11:47,610 --> 00:11:49,850
Ke was just being too impulsive earlier,

231
00:11:49,850 --> 00:11:50,770
When I go back,

232
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:53,250
I will certainly explain
everything to her.

233
00:11:54,010 --> 00:11:54,770
It's fine.

234
00:11:58,650 --> 00:11:59,390
By the way,

235
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:02,440
are you living with that Miss?

236
00:12:03,070 --> 00:12:04,250
I've been away from home for a long time,

237
00:12:04,250 --> 00:12:06,540
all my travel money has been spent,

238
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:09,020
so I'm currently staying at Ke's home.

239
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:11,680
After that argument just now,

240
00:12:12,220 --> 00:12:16,620
I imagine it would be difficult for you
to continue staying there, wouldn't it?

241
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,440
I feel that

242
00:12:23,650 --> 00:12:26,480
the misunderstanding in her heart
about me will be difficult to clear up.

243
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:28,290
She doesn't want us to meet again either.

244
00:12:28,290 --> 00:12:29,150
But

245
00:12:30,330 --> 00:12:31,640
I don't want to give up like this

246
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:32,970
and never see you again.

247
00:12:35,790 --> 00:12:36,830
If you trust me,

248
00:12:38,740 --> 00:12:40,070
leave everything to me,

249
00:12:40,090 --> 00:12:41,550
I'll solve your problems.

250
00:12:48,260 --> 00:12:49,190
Miss Qiyue,

251
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:51,700
give me a chance

252
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:54,740
to take care of you.

253
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:07,260
I appreciate your kindness.

254
00:13:08,270 --> 00:13:11,420
However, I've been staying
at Ke's home for many days,

255
00:13:11,860 --> 00:13:13,120
leaving just like that

256
00:13:13,840 --> 00:13:15,170
would be too heartless.

257
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:17,880
I understand.

258
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,110
If you're unhappy,

259
00:13:21,450 --> 00:13:22,850
you can come to me anytime.

260
00:13:22,850 --> 00:13:23,980
I'll always be here.

261
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:29,060
Here, have some tea.

262
00:13:36,760 --> 00:13:38,650
[Xibao Pavilion]

263
00:13:48,970 --> 00:13:49,590
Ke.

264
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:50,920
That's outrageous.

265
00:13:57,710 --> 00:13:59,710
Lu, I'm not talking about you.

266
00:13:59,950 --> 00:14:01,170
It's Marquis Wu'an.

267
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:02,890
Marquis Wu'an?

268
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:03,510
Exactly.

269
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:06,020
He's the one impersonating Mr. Lin Yuan.

270
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:08,230
Qiyue was deceived by him.
She doesn't believe me,

271
00:14:08,230 --> 00:14:10,960
but believes that bad man
is the real Mr. Lin Yuan.

272
00:14:12,820 --> 00:14:14,350
I find this suspicious too.

273
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,750
Why would Marquis Wu'an waste his time

274
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:17,980
deceiving Miss Yan?

275
00:14:18,010 --> 00:14:19,510
I find it strange as well.

276
00:14:19,990 --> 00:14:22,280
Marquis Wu'an
is such an unscrupulous person,

277
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:24,210
why would he target Qiyue, an outsider?

278
00:14:24,210 --> 00:14:25,630
And he loves money so much,

279
00:14:25,630 --> 00:14:28,070
yet Qiyue doesn't
even have money for an inn.

280
00:14:28,070 --> 00:14:30,070
I'm completely baffled by this too.

281
00:14:30,330 --> 00:14:30,990
No,

282
00:14:31,460 --> 00:14:32,850
I can't wait anymore.

283
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:34,180
Qiyue trusts him so much.

284
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:35,860
She can't wait to marry him.

285
00:14:36,390 --> 00:14:38,520
Never mind
that he's not the real Mr. Lin Yuan,

286
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:39,700
even if he were,

287
00:14:39,720 --> 00:14:41,570
I still couldn't let Qiyue marry him.

288
00:14:41,570 --> 00:14:43,100
So what do you plan to do, Ke?

289
00:14:43,950 --> 00:14:45,700
I'm having a fight with her right now.

290
00:14:45,700 --> 00:14:46,640
If I tell her,

291
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:48,190
she definitely won't believe me.

292
00:14:48,190 --> 00:14:50,120
She needs to figure it out herself.

293
00:14:56,890 --> 00:14:57,820
I've got an idea.

294
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,790
Lu, I'm leaving now.

295
00:15:00,510 --> 00:15:01,220
Ke.

296
00:15:07,690 --> 00:15:11,260
[Mount Qianya]

297
00:15:13,890 --> 00:15:17,220
[Mount Qianya]

298
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:18,330
Master.

299
00:15:20,550 --> 00:15:22,060
Master, something happened
at Mount Qianya.

300
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:22,980
A lot of soldiers

301
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:24,220
gather around Mount Qianya.

302
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:25,080
There are spies

303
00:15:25,090 --> 00:15:26,580
to inquire at every pass.

304
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:28,240
They seem to be ready
to attack the mountain at any time.

305
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:28,780
[Mount Qianya]

306
00:15:30,260 --> 00:15:32,780
Turns out Marquis Wu'an used a diversion,

307
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:35,580
all to claim Mount Qianya for himself.

308
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:37,610
Master, what should we do now?

309
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:42,310
Send a message to Zhuxi.

310
00:15:42,310 --> 00:15:43,980
Do not fight the enemy
for the land at the foot of the mountain,

311
00:15:43,980 --> 00:15:44,900
and do not act rashly.

312
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:46,470
Increase patrols and deploy carefully.

313
00:15:46,470 --> 00:15:47,000
Yes.

314
00:15:49,420 --> 00:15:50,270
Lu Yi.

315
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:01,450
[Mount Qianya]

316
00:16:29,870 --> 00:16:30,880
Take it to that person.

317
00:16:30,880 --> 00:16:31,410
Yes.

318
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:41,730
[Shi's Mansion]

319
00:16:43,630 --> 00:16:45,210
[Yachun House]

320
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,210
Ke.

321
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:53,610
[Shi's Mansion]

322
00:16:54,820 --> 00:16:57,870
Lu, what did you want to see me for?

323
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:02,520
I'm leaving.

324
00:17:05,550 --> 00:17:06,680
Where are you going?

325
00:17:07,599 --> 00:17:09,800
I'm setting off for Mount Qianya today.

326
00:17:14,849 --> 00:17:16,240
[Shi's Mansion]

327
00:17:17,430 --> 00:17:18,859
Why so suddenly?

328
00:17:19,530 --> 00:17:20,740
As reluctant as I am,

329
00:17:22,319 --> 00:17:23,940
I truly have urgent matters

330
00:17:24,630 --> 00:17:25,829
that I must attend to.

331
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:33,130
Ke.

332
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:34,800
♪ Although I can't remember ♪

333
00:17:34,800 --> 00:17:36,600
This is the seal I carved for you,

334
00:17:36,690 --> 00:17:37,180
though it's not finished yet.

335
00:17:37,180 --> 00:17:39,380
♪ Every tough day ♪

336
00:17:39,380 --> 00:17:40,560
I hope in the future,
whenever you complete a matchmaking case,

337
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,030
♪ But I've never forgotten ♪

338
00:17:42,150 --> 00:17:43,050
you can use it
to stamp your name on the Wedding Letter.

339
00:17:43,050 --> 00:17:46,820
♪ The first time I saw you ♪

340
00:17:48,050 --> 00:17:48,220
When will you come back?

341
00:17:48,220 --> 00:17:49,110
♪ Even if this love ♪

342
00:17:49,790 --> 00:17:50,330
♪ Is silent without days or nights ♪

343
00:17:50,330 --> 00:17:51,730
This trip to Mount Qianya

344
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:53,150
is to fulfill the mission
I told you about,

345
00:17:53,150 --> 00:17:54,390
♪ It has nothing to do
with the wind and the moon ♪

346
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:55,030
and to ease your parents' concerns.

347
00:17:55,030 --> 00:17:56,070
♪ From now on, as long as you're ♪

348
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:57,680
♪ Carefree without any restraint ♪

349
00:17:57,680 --> 00:17:58,630
After that, I can

350
00:17:58,660 --> 00:17:59,940
marry you with all the proper ceremony.

351
00:17:59,940 --> 00:18:01,790
♪ Enjoying this care ♪

352
00:18:02,840 --> 00:18:05,130
♪ Whether this vulgar world ♪

353
00:18:06,280 --> 00:18:08,670
♪ Will have any changes or not ♪

354
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:09,700
I don't want this now.

355
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:10,810
♪ I'm willing
to spend the rest of my life ♪

356
00:18:10,810 --> 00:18:12,140
I'll wait for you to return,

357
00:18:12,140 --> 00:18:12,970
♪ Protecting you ♪

358
00:18:12,970 --> 00:18:14,130
finish carving it,

359
00:18:15,180 --> 00:18:15,590
and give it to me in person.

360
00:18:15,590 --> 00:18:16,490
♪ Even if I might ♪

361
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:18,490
♪ Spoil you so much ♪

362
00:18:18,490 --> 00:18:20,480
All right, I promise you,

363
00:18:20,480 --> 00:18:21,810
♪ In front of you or from afar ♪

364
00:18:22,050 --> 00:18:22,380
I will definitely return safely.

365
00:18:22,380 --> 00:18:23,460
♪ Anyway, I'll still ♪

366
00:18:24,020 --> 00:18:26,460
♪ Love you wholeheartedly forever ♪

367
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:29,340
♪ I only have feelings for you ♪

368
00:18:30,390 --> 00:18:32,580
♪ Even though the world keeps changing ♪

369
00:18:33,710 --> 00:18:35,930
♪ It won't be the same as before ♪

370
00:18:36,980 --> 00:18:38,390
♪ Please remember ♪

371
00:18:39,430 --> 00:18:40,970
♪ That boy who was alone ♪

372
00:18:40,970 --> 00:18:42,500
You must keep your promise.

373
00:18:43,980 --> 00:18:44,130
You must come back.

374
00:18:44,130 --> 00:18:51,100
♪ He doesn't want to separate
from you anymore ♪

375
00:18:59,700 --> 00:19:00,500
I promise you.

376
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:22,500
Xianxian, Chongshan.

377
00:19:30,330 --> 00:19:31,040
Gentlemen.

378
00:19:31,950 --> 00:19:33,150
I have urgent matters

379
00:19:33,970 --> 00:19:35,710
and must return to Mount Qianya.

380
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:37,300
While I'm away from the capital,

381
00:19:37,300 --> 00:19:38,340
please,

382
00:19:39,220 --> 00:19:40,680
take good care of Ke for me.

383
00:19:43,210 --> 00:19:44,180
Don't worry.

384
00:19:44,390 --> 00:19:45,650
We'll protect Ke well.

385
00:19:46,870 --> 00:19:49,800
We won't let Ke suffer
even the slightest grievance.

386
00:19:51,190 --> 00:19:53,120
Then I can leave with peace of mind.

387
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:54,120
Until I return.

388
00:19:55,060 --> 00:19:56,590
I will definitely marry Ke.

389
00:19:57,820 --> 00:19:58,770
Lu,

390
00:20:00,150 --> 00:20:01,360
don't worry about me.

391
00:20:02,540 --> 00:20:04,500
I'll take good care of myself.

392
00:20:07,900 --> 00:20:09,420
Just come back soon.

393
00:20:14,550 --> 00:20:15,200
Young man,

394
00:20:15,810 --> 00:20:17,500
you'd better come back in one piece

395
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:18,640
to marry our Ke.

396
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:20,990
Otherwise, we won't let you go.

397
00:20:24,700 --> 00:20:26,030
My respected brothers,

398
00:20:26,570 --> 00:20:27,920
please accept my bow.

399
00:20:58,210 --> 00:21:03,200
[Yachun House]

400
00:21:05,910 --> 00:21:08,030
[Shi's Mansion]

401
00:21:22,740 --> 00:21:24,750
[Shi's Mansion]

402
00:21:40,870 --> 00:21:42,370
[Shi's Ancestral Hall]

403
00:21:53,970 --> 00:21:55,220
[Shi's Ancestral Hall]

404
00:21:59,870 --> 00:22:02,110
[Shi's Ancestral Hall]

405
00:22:19,710 --> 00:22:22,580
I often come here
to drink tea in my spare time.

406
00:22:23,330 --> 00:22:24,350
Here, Qiyue,

407
00:22:24,690 --> 00:22:27,620
try this Snow Mountain Green Tea
I've brewed for you.

408
00:22:35,090 --> 00:22:35,620
How is it?

409
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:37,380
It's quite good.

410
00:22:37,380 --> 00:22:38,480
Excuse me for interrupting,

411
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,160
Ke?

412
00:22:40,760 --> 00:22:41,550
Shi Fa'ke,

413
00:22:42,090 --> 00:22:43,020
what do you want?

414
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:44,400
Mr. Lin Yuan,

415
00:22:44,630 --> 00:22:46,230
I've long admired your reputation.

416
00:22:46,230 --> 00:22:47,070
This

417
00:22:47,800 --> 00:22:49,000
is one of your earlier works
from my collection.

418
00:22:49,000 --> 00:22:50,300
[High Mountains and Flowing Water]

419
00:22:50,300 --> 00:22:53,610
But I truly don't understand
the meaning behind this painting.

420
00:22:53,610 --> 00:22:55,340
Now that I've met you in person,

421
00:22:55,360 --> 00:22:57,760
I've come specifically for your guidance.

422
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:05,980
Please share your insights, Sir.

423
00:23:16,010 --> 00:23:18,940
Lofty mountains,
flowing waters, peaks upon peaks.

424
00:23:19,020 --> 00:23:19,210
[High Mountains and Flowing Water]

425
00:23:19,210 --> 00:23:21,610
The beauty of mountains
lies in their form,

426
00:23:21,650 --> 00:23:24,180
while the beauty of water
lies in its essence.

427
00:23:25,260 --> 00:23:28,460
Ordinary people only see
the beauty of these landscapes,

428
00:23:28,540 --> 00:23:29,800
but they don't realize

429
00:23:30,140 --> 00:23:32,270
they represent the wounds in my heart.

430
00:23:32,690 --> 00:23:34,900
The higher the mountain,
the more solitary its existence,

431
00:23:34,900 --> 00:23:37,700
and the clearer the water,
the fewer fish it holds.

432
00:23:37,930 --> 00:23:39,650
I have no companions, no friends.

433
00:23:39,650 --> 00:23:39,770
[High Mountains and Flowing Water]

434
00:23:39,770 --> 00:23:42,410
This loneliness of being too refined
for common taste,

435
00:23:42,410 --> 00:23:44,210
who could possibly understand?

436
00:23:46,460 --> 00:23:47,240
Is that so?

437
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:50,890
I bought this painting
at the Yunlou Painting Shop.

438
00:23:51,590 --> 00:23:53,490
It was painted by someone else.

439
00:23:54,220 --> 00:23:55,870
Since you like it so much,

440
00:23:55,890 --> 00:23:57,550
you're welcome to go buy more.

441
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:03,010
I've painted countless works in my life,

442
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:06,350
often creating
casual pieces when I'm drunk.

443
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:08,830
These landscapes are quite ordinary.

444
00:24:09,300 --> 00:24:11,690
To be honest, I don't quite remember them.

445
00:24:11,810 --> 00:24:14,270
Yes, you're absolutely right.

446
00:24:14,500 --> 00:24:17,010
It's normal for scholars
to enjoy drinking.

447
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:18,590
With countless paintings,

448
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:20,650
it's understandable to forget some.

449
00:24:31,260 --> 00:24:34,030
Please, Mr. Lin Yuan,
grace us with your calligraphy.

450
00:24:34,030 --> 00:24:35,480
If I could have the honor

451
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:37,020
of you writing
an inscription for me in person,

452
00:24:37,020 --> 00:24:39,100
I would truly
have no regrets in this life.

453
00:24:39,100 --> 00:24:41,100
Why should I write anything for you?

454
00:24:41,430 --> 00:24:42,480
Mr. Lin Yuan,

455
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:44,700
I'd like to see it too.

456
00:24:51,180 --> 00:24:52,110
Please go ahead.

457
00:24:56,160 --> 00:24:58,840
Very well,
since Miss Qiyue wants to see it,

458
00:24:58,990 --> 00:25:00,190
I'll grant your wish.

459
00:25:10,930 --> 00:25:11,520
This...

460
00:25:12,530 --> 00:25:14,510
The fan is wet now,

461
00:25:15,540 --> 00:25:16,380
I'm terribly sorry,

462
00:25:16,380 --> 00:25:17,380
it wasn't intentional.

463
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:18,540
It's nothing.

464
00:25:18,690 --> 00:25:19,540
Come.

465
00:25:19,570 --> 00:25:20,670
It's alright, Lord Marquis.

466
00:25:20,670 --> 00:25:22,480
I brought many fans,

467
00:25:22,820 --> 00:25:26,340
round fans, palm-leaf fans,
paper fans, bamboo fans, all kinds.

468
00:25:26,340 --> 00:25:27,800
I wasn't sure which one you'd prefer,

469
00:25:27,800 --> 00:25:29,000
so I brought them all.

470
00:25:29,080 --> 00:25:30,050
Especially this one.

471
00:25:30,050 --> 00:25:30,690
This one here

472
00:25:30,690 --> 00:25:33,950
is made with waterproof silk
for a waterproof fan surface.

473
00:25:34,210 --> 00:25:36,180
Sir, please write something on it.

474
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:45,920
Shi Fa'ke, this is outrageous!

475
00:25:47,770 --> 00:25:49,610
Qiyue, let's go.

476
00:25:50,010 --> 00:25:50,540
Let's go.

477
00:26:04,530 --> 00:26:04,710
Ke, how could I
run into such a con artist?

478
00:26:04,710 --> 00:26:08,950
[Shi's Ancestral Hall]

479
00:26:08,950 --> 00:26:10,810
I only wanted to find Mr. Lin Yuan,

480
00:26:10,930 --> 00:26:12,590
why is this path so difficult?

481
00:26:12,980 --> 00:26:13,790
Could it be

482
00:26:13,910 --> 00:26:16,510
that Mr. Lin Yuan and I
are truly not meant to be?

483
00:26:16,590 --> 00:26:18,700
I won't really end up alone
for the rest of my life, will I?

484
00:26:18,700 --> 00:26:19,800
How could that happen?

485
00:26:19,800 --> 00:26:22,080
With me around,
how could you possibly grow old alone?

486
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:23,850
You're just too impatient,

487
00:26:23,870 --> 00:26:25,820
that's why you've become
a target for opportunists.

488
00:26:25,820 --> 00:26:27,300
You must learn from this,

489
00:26:27,330 --> 00:26:29,060
don't be so impulsive anymore,

490
00:26:29,120 --> 00:26:30,960
so I won't have to worry about you.

491
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:33,080
I was wrong to blame you before,

492
00:26:33,850 --> 00:26:34,590
I'm sorry.

493
00:26:35,910 --> 00:26:36,750
Qiyue,

494
00:26:37,010 --> 00:26:39,460
there's nothing wrong
with admiring Mr. Lin Yuan.

495
00:26:39,460 --> 00:26:41,000
But have you considered that

496
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,870
the Mr. Lin Yuan behind these paintings

497
00:26:42,870 --> 00:26:44,280
is also a real person?

498
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:47,460
Marriage isn't just about romance,

499
00:26:47,940 --> 00:26:49,160
you'll also have to face

500
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:51,160
all kinds of daily chores together.

501
00:26:51,190 --> 00:26:53,050
If you don't truly know each other

502
00:26:53,050 --> 00:26:54,750
and it's just a momentary passion,

503
00:26:54,750 --> 00:26:56,330
how can you spend a lifetime together?

504
00:26:56,330 --> 00:26:57,510
Where am I supposed to find someone

505
00:26:57,510 --> 00:26:59,160
to spend my life with?

506
00:27:00,470 --> 00:27:04,150
Qiyue, one day, you'll meet someone
who truly loves you as you love them,

507
00:27:04,150 --> 00:27:05,880
and spend a lifetime together.

508
00:27:06,290 --> 00:27:07,000
Really?

509
00:27:08,090 --> 00:27:10,220
Will fate arrange such a person for me?

510
00:27:10,250 --> 00:27:11,860
This can't be left to fate,

511
00:27:11,890 --> 00:27:13,260
and certainly not to Mr. Lin Yuan.

512
00:27:13,260 --> 00:27:14,500
Then I can leave it to you, right?

513
00:27:14,500 --> 00:27:15,330
No.

514
00:27:17,670 --> 00:27:18,730
This matter

515
00:27:18,810 --> 00:27:20,850
can only be entrusted to your own heart.

516
00:27:20,850 --> 00:27:23,050
I can only help facilitate a good match.

517
00:27:23,220 --> 00:27:24,440
Who you actually like

518
00:27:24,580 --> 00:27:25,850
is for you to decide.

519
00:27:28,500 --> 00:27:29,300
I understand.

520
00:27:29,910 --> 00:27:31,730
I was wrong before.

521
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:34,930
Please don't be angry with me anymore.

522
00:27:35,770 --> 00:27:37,030
I'm not angry anymore.

523
00:27:43,460 --> 00:27:45,060
It's that Shi Fa'ke again!

524
00:27:45,240 --> 00:27:46,440
I was just one step away

525
00:27:46,440 --> 00:27:48,130
from marrying Yan Qiyue.

526
00:27:48,150 --> 00:27:49,770
This time I absolutely
won't let her get away!

527
00:27:49,770 --> 00:27:51,230
Lord Marquis, please calm your anger,

528
00:27:51,230 --> 00:27:53,520
we've received news from Mount Qianya.

529
00:27:54,420 --> 00:27:55,340
How is it?

530
00:27:55,530 --> 00:27:57,070
Everything is in position,

531
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,720
awaiting your orders, My Lord.

532
00:27:58,720 --> 00:27:59,310
Good.

533
00:27:59,690 --> 00:28:00,690
Relay my command:

534
00:28:01,330 --> 00:28:03,260
Attack Mount Qianya immediately.

535
00:28:03,260 --> 00:28:05,510
I want to destroy his power outside

536
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:06,760
and his wings.

537
00:28:08,330 --> 00:28:11,440
I will kill those

538
00:28:12,690 --> 00:28:14,030
who oppose me.

539
00:28:14,380 --> 00:28:16,440
My Lord, you're heaven's chosen one,

540
00:28:16,670 --> 00:28:19,870
you will surely be invincible
and achieve swift victory!

541
00:28:22,750 --> 00:28:25,690
Qiyue, this play today is really good.

542
00:28:25,810 --> 00:28:26,870
After you watch it,

543
00:28:26,890 --> 00:28:29,350
you'll definitely forget
all your troubles.

544
00:28:29,350 --> 00:28:30,680
I hope so.

545
00:28:31,020 --> 00:28:32,360
Ladies,

546
00:28:32,390 --> 00:28:34,070
just the two of you is no fun.

547
00:28:34,090 --> 00:28:34,730
Why don't...

548
00:28:34,730 --> 00:28:35,520
That's right.

549
00:28:35,520 --> 00:28:37,000
Why don't we join you?

550
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:40,510
-Where are you going?
-Let me tell you.

551
00:28:40,510 --> 00:28:41,620
My eldest brother is a constable.

552
00:28:41,620 --> 00:28:42,250
so don't try anything.

553
00:28:42,250 --> 00:28:42,890
Go away!

554
00:28:42,910 --> 00:28:44,000
Even constables have to be reasonable,

555
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:47,100
-We just want to make friends with you.
-Yeah. Since when is that against the law?

556
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:48,210
Who wants to be friends with you?

557
00:28:48,210 --> 00:28:49,040
Let's go!

558
00:28:50,020 --> 00:28:51,240
Don't run, Miss.

559
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:54,250
Qiyue!

560
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:57,070
Mr. Huang!

561
00:28:57,070 --> 00:28:58,470
Miss Qiyue, run quickly!

562
00:28:58,880 --> 00:29:00,000
Don't interfere!

563
00:29:04,910 --> 00:29:05,960
Lu Yi?

564
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:26,170
Get lost!

565
00:29:27,380 --> 00:29:29,570
Thankfully this young hero helped them.

566
00:29:29,570 --> 00:29:31,070
Miss Shi, are you alright?

567
00:29:31,200 --> 00:29:33,050
I'm fine, thanks to you.

568
00:29:33,080 --> 00:29:35,690
But why didn't you leave?

569
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,170
The Chief asked me to stay

570
00:29:37,170 --> 00:29:38,280
to protect you.

571
00:29:41,460 --> 00:29:43,980
Ke, this is Mr. Huang.

572
00:29:44,300 --> 00:29:45,750
He's the second friend

573
00:29:45,860 --> 00:29:47,990
I've made since coming to the capital.

574
00:29:48,010 --> 00:29:49,010
Hello, Mr. Huang.

575
00:29:49,060 --> 00:29:50,140
My name is Shi Fa'ke,

576
00:29:50,140 --> 00:29:51,600
I'm a marriage broker from
the Official Matchmaking Agency.

577
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:54,250
Thank you for your help
just now, Mr. Huang.

578
00:29:54,330 --> 00:29:55,390
I'm flattered, Miss Shi.

579
00:29:55,390 --> 00:29:57,250
It was nothing worth mentioning.

580
00:29:58,680 --> 00:29:59,400
Miss Qiyue,

581
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:01,040
it's been a while

582
00:30:01,170 --> 00:30:02,370
since we last met.

583
00:30:05,090 --> 00:30:06,040
Let's not talk about that.

584
00:30:06,040 --> 00:30:08,020
Let's chat about something more pleasant.

585
00:30:08,020 --> 00:30:10,200
You don't come
to this theater often, do you?

586
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,790
Besides the good performances here,

587
00:30:11,790 --> 00:30:13,920
the pastries are quite delicious too.

588
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:15,140
Then let me guess

589
00:30:15,530 --> 00:30:17,190
what your favorite pastry is.

590
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:19,520
Brown sugar cake.

591
00:30:21,960 --> 00:30:23,500
Here, have some tea first.

592
00:30:26,270 --> 00:30:27,730
Miss Qiyue, you like these,

593
00:30:27,730 --> 00:30:28,880
go ahead and try one,

594
00:30:28,940 --> 00:30:30,900
but be careful, they're a bit hot.

595
00:30:30,930 --> 00:30:31,480
Here.

596
00:30:32,040 --> 00:30:33,040
Try one yourself.

597
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:39,770
Mr. Huang,

598
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:41,540
you look unfamiliar.

599
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:42,930
Are you from the capital?

600
00:30:42,930 --> 00:30:44,140
Where are you staying now?

601
00:30:44,140 --> 00:30:46,470
I'm temporarily staying at Qingfeng Inn.

602
00:30:47,310 --> 00:30:49,360
So you're not from the capital.

603
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:52,200
Then, Mr. Huang, where is your hometown?

604
00:30:58,300 --> 00:30:59,430
Ke.

605
00:30:59,450 --> 00:31:00,760
Don't try to matchmake

606
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:02,580
every person you meet, will you?

607
00:31:03,870 --> 00:31:05,940
Mr. Huang, what a coincidence,

608
00:31:06,290 --> 00:31:07,210
Qiyue

609
00:31:07,240 --> 00:31:08,880
also stayed at Qingfeng Inn before.

610
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,870
However, she was there for Mr. Lin...

611
00:31:10,870 --> 00:31:11,430
Ke.

612
00:31:17,180 --> 00:31:18,510
Have some pastries too.

613
00:31:21,980 --> 00:31:23,110
Have another piece.

614
00:31:24,710 --> 00:31:26,570
This one is delicious too, try it.

615
00:31:26,970 --> 00:31:28,630
Judging by Qiyue's reaction,

616
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:31,870
she seems to have
special feelings for Mr. Huang.

617
00:31:31,870 --> 00:31:34,980
[Xibao Pavilion]

618
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:41,640
Yesterday's new shipment.

619
00:31:41,640 --> 00:31:42,790
Haven't they been displayed yet?

620
00:31:42,790 --> 00:31:44,480
I think they're underneath that.

621
00:31:44,480 --> 00:31:45,350
Let me look again.

622
00:31:45,350 --> 00:31:46,160
Is this it?

623
00:31:46,980 --> 00:31:48,060
This seems to be it.

624
00:31:48,150 --> 00:31:50,150
The quantity is correct too, right?

625
00:31:57,190 --> 00:31:58,930
The people from our Xibao Pavilion

626
00:31:58,930 --> 00:32:01,330
are all being lured away
by your Shi family.

627
00:32:17,520 --> 00:32:18,450
Ke, you're here.

628
00:32:19,530 --> 00:32:19,660
[To Shi Fa'ke]

629
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:21,390
A letter from the Chief for you.

630
00:32:25,290 --> 00:32:26,920
Mount Qianya is far away,

631
00:32:27,260 --> 00:32:28,420
and even though the Chief was in a hurry,

632
00:32:28,420 --> 00:32:29,930
he still took time to write to you,

633
00:32:29,930 --> 00:32:32,120
showing how much he misses you.

634
00:32:35,120 --> 00:32:36,680
[To Shi Fa'ke]

635
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:38,530
Well, I'll let you
read your letter in peace.

636
00:32:38,530 --> 00:32:39,930
I need to get back to work.

637
00:32:52,190 --> 00:32:52,840
Ke.

638
00:32:53,850 --> 00:32:54,970
My dear Ke.

639
00:32:55,930 --> 00:32:57,590
May this letter find you well.

640
00:32:58,220 --> 00:33:01,340
Days apart, and my longing grows stronger.

641
00:33:02,290 --> 00:33:03,550
Without you by my side,

642
00:33:04,010 --> 00:33:05,830
everything has lost its flavor.

643
00:33:08,390 --> 00:33:11,590
The sunrises and sunsets on Mount Qianya
that I once loved so much

644
00:33:11,590 --> 00:33:13,120
have all lost their luster.

645
00:33:14,570 --> 00:33:15,910
Since we first met,

646
00:33:16,740 --> 00:33:18,600
I've never felt such loneliness.

647
00:33:19,910 --> 00:33:20,630
I miss you.

648
00:33:22,470 --> 00:33:23,230
I miss you.

649
00:33:25,860 --> 00:33:30,960
[Liuhe Pavilion]

650
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:45,850
Qiyue, what are you thinking about?

651
00:33:47,700 --> 00:33:48,520
Ke,

652
00:33:49,090 --> 00:33:50,640
I've been like this lately.

653
00:33:51,130 --> 00:33:52,590
Sometimes I'm happy,

654
00:33:53,610 --> 00:33:54,710
but other times...

655
00:33:57,130 --> 00:33:58,790
I'm just so conflicted.

656
00:34:00,430 --> 00:34:03,410
Qiyue, you must
have feelings for Mr. Huang.

657
00:34:03,620 --> 00:34:04,750
That's impossible.

658
00:34:05,160 --> 00:34:06,730
We just get along well.

659
00:34:06,750 --> 00:34:08,440
We both admire Mr. Lin Yuan,

660
00:34:08,530 --> 00:34:10,530
that's why we have good conversations.

661
00:34:10,530 --> 00:34:11,190
I...

662
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:14,010
I won't marry anyone but Mr. Lin Yuan.

663
00:34:14,010 --> 00:34:14,650
Qiyue,

664
00:34:15,250 --> 00:34:16,820
you don't need to explain to me

665
00:34:16,820 --> 00:34:18,020
or try to convince me.

666
00:34:18,350 --> 00:34:19,810
Deep down, only you

667
00:34:19,830 --> 00:34:21,230
know who you really like.

668
00:34:22,170 --> 00:34:23,900
You just need to ask yourself

669
00:34:24,060 --> 00:34:26,120
if Mr. Huang has a place in your heart.

670
00:34:31,210 --> 00:34:33,300
If you have no feelings for Mr. Huang,

671
00:34:33,679 --> 00:34:35,969
then you shouldn't see each other anymore,

672
00:34:35,969 --> 00:34:37,050
to avoid giving him

673
00:34:37,070 --> 00:34:38,530
unrealistic expectations.

674
00:34:38,530 --> 00:34:40,389
That wouldn't be good for anyone.

675
00:34:42,350 --> 00:34:43,940
I don't know.

676
00:34:44,989 --> 00:34:45,260
[Liuhe Pavilion]

677
00:34:45,260 --> 00:34:47,060
I'm unhappy when I don't see him.

678
00:34:47,260 --> 00:34:47,949
But

679
00:34:48,310 --> 00:34:49,929
if I'm supposed to give up Mr. Lin Yuan,

680
00:34:49,929 --> 00:34:51,060
I can't accept that.

681
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,440
I'm so confused,

682
00:34:52,730 --> 00:34:54,929
I don't know what my heart really wants.

683
00:34:58,450 --> 00:34:59,220
It's okay.

684
00:35:00,030 --> 00:35:01,560
Just give me a few more days,

685
00:35:01,740 --> 00:35:03,180
I'll definitely find a way

686
00:35:03,180 --> 00:35:05,580
to help you understand your true feelings.

687
00:35:22,370 --> 00:35:23,430
Miss Shi.

688
00:35:23,650 --> 00:35:25,250
Your instructions, please.

689
00:35:27,450 --> 00:35:28,190
Come.

690
00:35:35,210 --> 00:35:36,060
Do you understand?

691
00:35:36,060 --> 00:35:37,120
Yes, I understand.

692
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:44,050
Qiyue, look at these paintings

693
00:35:44,070 --> 00:35:45,870
and see if any are by Mr. Lin Yuan?

694
00:35:46,530 --> 00:35:47,500
Not again.

695
00:35:47,530 --> 00:35:48,560
I refuse to choose.

696
00:35:48,560 --> 00:35:49,660
Last time there wasn't a single one,

697
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:50,850
and you're trying
to fool me with this trick again.

698
00:35:50,850 --> 00:35:53,000
I promise I'm not joking.

699
00:35:53,030 --> 00:35:56,160
There really is an authentic work
by Mr. Lin Yuan in here.

700
00:36:14,100 --> 00:36:15,430
[Having Equal Status in Marriage]

701
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:21,330
I can't tell.

702
00:36:21,350 --> 00:36:23,510
They all look similar to me.

703
00:36:23,680 --> 00:36:24,400
Look.

704
00:36:24,420 --> 00:36:26,780
Even if there really is an authentic work
by Mr. Lin Yuan in there,

705
00:36:26,780 --> 00:36:28,480
you still wouldn't be able to identify it.

706
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:32,040
Am I truly not destined
to connect with Mr. Lin Yuan?

707
00:36:37,050 --> 00:36:37,700
Come here.

708
00:36:42,770 --> 00:36:44,610
Ke, what are you doing now?

709
00:36:45,270 --> 00:36:46,790
There are five young men here.

710
00:36:46,790 --> 00:36:48,510
Let's see if you can identify

711
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,670
which one is Mr. Huang just by looking.

712
00:36:50,670 --> 00:36:52,000
Mr. Huang is right here?

713
00:37:18,490 --> 00:37:19,200
Qiyue.

714
00:37:19,790 --> 00:37:21,550
You said you admire Mr. Lin Yuan

715
00:37:21,610 --> 00:37:22,940
through his paintings,

716
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:24,030
yet you can't tell

717
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:25,840
which one is his authentic work.

718
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:27,530
But with just your eyes,

719
00:37:27,530 --> 00:37:29,890
you immediately recognized Mr. Huang.

720
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:38,270
Qiyue.

721
00:37:39,850 --> 00:37:42,450
Your heart has already
made the choice for you.

722
00:37:42,630 --> 00:37:44,240
Do you prefer the painter

723
00:37:44,470 --> 00:37:46,730
or the person appreciating art with you?

724
00:37:48,950 --> 00:37:50,490
Eyes never lie.

725
00:37:51,300 --> 00:37:52,130
You must have seen

726
00:37:52,130 --> 00:37:54,310
his feelings for you just now.

727
00:37:54,680 --> 00:37:55,330
Qiyue.

728
00:37:56,100 --> 00:37:58,700
Why not look at
who's already by your side?

729
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:08,760
My Lord.

730
00:38:09,330 --> 00:38:09,950
My Lord.

731
00:38:09,970 --> 00:38:10,480
Speak.

732
00:38:11,130 --> 00:38:12,740
I bring two pieces of news.

733
00:38:12,820 --> 00:38:13,590
What news?

734
00:38:13,640 --> 00:38:14,450
First,

735
00:38:14,590 --> 00:38:17,080
that person hasn't
attended court for several days,

736
00:38:17,080 --> 00:38:19,700
surely fearing your lordship's power,

737
00:38:19,940 --> 00:38:21,270
his time is running out.

738
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:24,720
Your ascension to the throne

739
00:38:24,740 --> 00:38:26,070
is just a matter of time.

740
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:27,970
What's the other news?

741
00:38:27,970 --> 00:38:29,200
The second is

742
00:38:29,410 --> 00:38:32,770
Lu Chi has departed for Mount Qianya.

743
00:38:34,740 --> 00:38:35,360
[Mount Qianya]

744
00:38:35,360 --> 00:38:36,220
Good.

745
00:38:36,650 --> 00:38:39,630
Everything is in my plan.

746
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:42,740
As long as I can catch Lu Chi's weakness

747
00:38:43,270 --> 00:38:45,520
and control Shi Fa'ke,

748
00:38:45,810 --> 00:38:47,010
if I ask him to go east,

749
00:38:47,220 --> 00:38:48,750
he wouldn't dare to go west.

750
00:38:48,750 --> 00:38:51,580
I'm going to catch Shi Fa'ke now.

751
00:38:51,780 --> 00:38:52,490
Go now.

752
00:38:52,510 --> 00:38:52,990
Yes.

753
00:39:13,960 --> 00:39:15,140
Lu.

754
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:21,620
Lu.

755
00:39:22,820 --> 00:39:23,520
Ke.

756
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:15,890
Something terrible has happened!

757
00:40:16,430 --> 00:40:17,470
Uncle, Aunt!

758
00:40:17,500 --> 00:40:19,070
There's a squad of soldiers outside

759
00:40:19,070 --> 00:40:21,130
saying they're here to arrest Fa'ke.

760
00:40:21,810 --> 00:40:22,500
Me?

761
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:29,550
The Military Headquarters
has been ordered to arrest Shi Fa'ke.

762
00:40:29,550 --> 00:40:31,410
Hand over Shi Fa'ke immediately.

763
00:40:31,930 --> 00:40:33,130
I am Shi Fa'ke.

764
00:40:33,150 --> 00:40:33,750
Ke!

765
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:35,240
What crime has my daughter committed?

766
00:40:35,240 --> 00:40:37,040
How dare you barge in
and arrest people like this?

767
00:40:37,040 --> 00:40:38,260
Do you have an arrest warrant?

768
00:40:38,260 --> 00:40:39,510
Breaking into a private home,
according to the law...

769
00:40:39,510 --> 00:40:41,040
Everyone else, stand back!

770
00:40:42,240 --> 00:40:43,300
Weapons don't discriminate.

771
00:40:43,300 --> 00:40:45,720
It would be unfortunate
if someone got hurt.

772
00:40:45,720 --> 00:40:46,760
Let me tell you this.

773
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:48,950
You're not taking my daughter away today.

774
00:40:48,950 --> 00:40:50,210
I don't care what authority you represent,

775
00:40:50,210 --> 00:40:51,510
you're not taking Ke away today.

776
00:40:51,510 --> 00:40:52,370
Enough talk!

777
00:40:52,970 --> 00:40:53,490
Take her away!

778
00:40:53,490 --> 00:40:54,000
-Yes.
-Yes.

779
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:54,400
You...

780
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:54,760
Move aside!

781
00:40:54,760 --> 00:40:55,740
What are you doing?

782
00:40:55,740 --> 00:40:57,270
-Move!
-What are you doing?

783
00:40:58,110 --> 00:40:58,970
What are you doing?

784
00:40:58,970 --> 00:40:59,520
Don't be so disrespectful!

785
00:40:59,520 --> 00:40:59,970
Move aside!

786
00:40:59,970 --> 00:41:00,690
Don't go too far! Step back!

787
00:41:00,690 --> 00:41:01,520
What do you think you're doing?

788
00:41:01,520 --> 00:41:02,210
Stop!

789
00:41:02,270 --> 00:41:02,690
Get out of the way!

790
00:41:02,690 --> 00:41:03,170
Stop!

791
00:41:06,030 --> 00:41:06,960
I'll go with you.

792
00:41:07,190 --> 00:41:07,920
Ke!

793
00:41:08,270 --> 00:41:09,610
No, you can't! Don't!

794
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:11,170
Ke, are you sure about this?

795
00:41:11,330 --> 00:41:12,610
I have nothing to hide.

796
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:14,400
I've done nothing wrong.

797
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:15,930
They'll have to release me
sooner or later.

798
00:41:15,930 --> 00:41:16,600
Fa'ke!

799
00:41:18,850 --> 00:41:19,710
-Let's go.
-Ke.

800
00:41:19,810 --> 00:41:20,270
Ke.

801
00:41:20,290 --> 00:41:21,330
-Ke.
-Ke.

802
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:23,140
-Aunt.
-Madam.

803
00:41:23,170 --> 00:41:23,790
Mother.

804
00:41:24,220 --> 00:41:25,610
Father, Mother.

805
00:41:25,700 --> 00:41:26,930
Miss Qiyue, Qin'er.

806
00:41:27,010 --> 00:41:28,610
We'll find a way to rescue Ke.

807
00:41:28,730 --> 00:41:30,240
Chongshan, let's go.

808
00:41:30,670 --> 00:41:31,610
Wait.

809
00:41:32,330 --> 00:41:34,220
Xianxian, Chongshan, let me come with you.

810
00:41:34,220 --> 00:41:34,810
Alright.

811
00:41:56,000 --> 00:41:58,140
Greetings, Master.

812
00:42:02,110 --> 00:42:04,250
This Marquis Wu'an has gone too far.

813
00:42:05,150 --> 00:42:05,920
Chi.

814
00:42:05,970 --> 00:42:07,710
The enemy forces greatly outnumber ours.

815
00:42:07,710 --> 00:42:09,270
Our recent engagements with them

816
00:42:09,270 --> 00:42:10,700
have resulted in heavy casualties.

817
00:42:10,700 --> 00:42:12,500
Please punish me for my failure.

818
00:42:16,230 --> 00:42:17,360
You've worked hard.

819
00:42:17,970 --> 00:42:19,230
This isn't your fault.

820
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:21,780
Li Ang is leading their troops this time,

821
00:42:21,970 --> 00:42:24,070
a stubborn and brutal man.

822
00:42:24,520 --> 00:42:26,310
At least you've engaged with them

823
00:42:26,310 --> 00:42:27,840
and learned about their situation,

824
00:42:27,840 --> 00:42:30,190
which will be very beneficial
for our future battles.

825
00:42:30,190 --> 00:42:31,670
They've sent their elite troops

826
00:42:31,670 --> 00:42:32,880
to cut off the capital's retreat route.

827
00:42:32,880 --> 00:42:33,590
Perfect,

828
00:42:34,540 --> 00:42:36,350
we'll make sure they never return,

829
00:42:36,350 --> 00:42:38,740
and free the capital from any concerns.

830
00:42:39,170 --> 00:42:41,080
Chi, you have a plan?

831
00:42:42,600 --> 00:42:43,710
Officers, attention!

832
00:42:43,710 --> 00:42:44,510
Yes, Sir!

833
00:42:45,180 --> 00:42:46,530
Our forces are outnumbered,

834
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:49,310
a direct confrontation
would surely lead to defeat,

835
00:42:49,310 --> 00:42:52,170
so we must use
Mount Qianya's terrain to our advantage.

