00:42:52,170 --> 00:42:53,230
Send out the order:

837
00:42:53,270 --> 00:42:54,910
immediately send men
down the mountain with great fanfare,

838
00:42:54,910 --> 00:42:56,050
buying and stockpiling provisions,

839
00:42:56,050 --> 00:42:58,660
carrying war drums
and banners, shouting loudly,

840
00:42:58,660 --> 00:43:01,280
making the enemy believe
we have many troops and ample supplies.

841
00:43:01,280 --> 00:43:02,390
Before their supplies arrive,

842
00:43:02,390 --> 00:43:04,050
they won't dare to make any rash moves.

843
00:43:04,050 --> 00:43:05,200
Once their supplies arrive,

844
00:43:05,200 --> 00:43:07,400
we'll engage them in a war of attrition,

845
00:43:07,710 --> 00:43:10,510
even if we can't defeat them,
we'll wear them down.

846
00:43:11,830 --> 00:43:13,040
But I'm worried

847
00:43:13,070 --> 00:43:14,220
that if this drags on too long,

848
00:43:14,220 --> 00:43:15,760
we might not be able to hold out.

849
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:16,540
Don't worry,

850
00:43:16,570 --> 00:43:18,510
we certainly won't
just sit and wait for death.

851
00:43:18,510 --> 00:43:19,260
Zhuxi,

852
00:43:20,150 --> 00:43:21,640
I have a plan now

853
00:43:22,270 --> 00:43:25,010
that will dampen their spirits.
